videos.headline: Boise State scores 75-yard TD in first 10 seconds of game
videos.description: Jack Sears isn't wasting any time as he fires a long pass to CT Thomas for a 75-yard touchdown in the first ten seconds of the Broncos' matchup against Air Force.
